name: CaptureBrightnessLevelType
description: The brightness level of the video image captured by the local camera.

parameters.Invalid: -1: The SDK does not detect the brightness level of the video image. Wait a few seconds to get the brightness level from captureBrightnessLevel in the next callback.

parameters.Normal: 0: The brightness level of the video image is normal.

parameters.Bright: 1: The brightness level of the video image is too bright.

parameters.Dark: 2: The brightness level of the video image is too dark.
